text.jpText:
はぁ～怖いわぁ～。
自分の実力が怖いわぁ～。
text.enText:
Huh～ I'm scared! I'm scared 
of my own abilities!

text.jpText:
なんやなんや、聞きたいんか？
しゃーないなぁ。特別に聞かしたるわ！
ウチはなぁ――
text.enText:
What the heck, you want to hear it? I'll make 
you a special offer! I'll make you a special 
offer! I'll tell you what…

text.jpText:
同時に開催された3つのセール！
その3つともを完ッ璧にハシゴして、
ぜーんぶのセール品を買うてみせたんや！
text.enText:
Three sales held at the same time! I went to 
all three of them and bought everything on 
sale! I bought everything on sale!

text.jpText:
いやぁ～アンタにも見したかったわ。
商店街の人混みを駆け抜ける
“白い稲妻”の勇姿を……！
text.enText:
I wish you could have seen it. I wish you 
could have seen the courage of the "White 
Lightning" as it ran through the crowds in 
the shopping district: ……!
